<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Scary Movie 3 - In the Hood</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In &quot;Scary Movie 3,&quot; George has just seriously impressed a crowd with his battle-rapping skills. But when he puts a hood over his head and looks like a KKK member (&quot;Yo, we're in the hood now!&quot;) and does what looks like a Nazi salute, the only person that's surprised when they toss him out a window is him.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="gz6mr1">
